{"tid":48061,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"仆你條街 蚊真係好撚可惡","createTime":"2016-12-20T20:41:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T03:19:22.000Z","uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fcfeb558fcb718322774cc71e63768418795c040","tid":48061,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T20:41:04.000Z","msg":"屌<br />\n啲蚊係咪識瞬間轉移???<br />\n訓到三點半比蚊咬到痕醒左<br />\n咁我開燈打蚊啦<br />\n每次見到隻蚊打埋去個下就消失左<br />\n反反複複已經就十次<br />\n點解會咁！！！！！ <br />\n我想訓教啊你老尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解12月尾仲咁熱啲蚊仲生存緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e5bfbf06a9c9e58d61f6a5432c62e419c24dc6","tid":48061,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T20:45:22.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"3df2ff765d78cf3db1855e0233bbede7e31e7c53","tid":48061,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T20:48:34.000Z","msg":"你打法錯<br />\n一係你開弱光打<br />\n一係你feel下邊到痕/痛就打，唔好R<br />\n再唔係你聽到有聲就出力一掌打落隻耳到<br />\n<br />\n我都係人教我感覺比蚊咬，慢慢你會好快feel到蚊咬個感覺，及早打死佢"},{"pid":"7b34bf1791085e6c879e9a7eb7f70397b3706285","tid":48061,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T20:49:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Agger</blockquote><br />\n你屋企咁嘈應該可以打死哂啲蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19937685b528d8d88bbff4970443361d53f623d","tid":48061,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T20:50:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Agger</blockquote><br />\n你屋企咁嘈應該可以打死哂啲蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n訓左了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c6e57aa10c6fc24013336f4563f889770622e35","tid":48061,"uid":53272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T20:51:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你打法錯<br />\n一係你開弱光打<br />\n一係你feel下邊到痕/痛就打，唔好R<br />\n再唔係你聽到